# >>> Combined Gemini & Google AI Studio Ruleset <<<
# Description: Merged ruleset for iOS Gemini APP, Web, and Developer AI Studio.

# 1. Gemini & Bard Core Domains (App & Web)
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,gemini.google
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,gemini.google.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,bard.google.com

# 2. Generative AI & Developer Platforms (Google AI Studio / Makersuite)
DOMAIN,ai.google.dev
DOMAIN,alkalimakersuite-pa.clients6.google.com
DOMAIN,makersuite.google.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,generativeai.google
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,generativelanguage
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,colab
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,developerprofiles

# 3. Google DeepMind Ecosystem
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,deepmind.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,deepmind.google

# 4. Backend APIs & Frameworks
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,proactivebackend-pa.googleapis.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,apis.google.com
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,googleapis

# 5. Essential App Support (Accounts & Resources - Missing in image)
DOMAIN,accounts.google.com
